Package workerManagerResourceSpotAllocation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GatheringSource
    GatheringSource.java --- An Interface specifying a single gathering source or, addressing minerals, a group of possible gathering sources.
    IResourceManager
    IResourceManager.java --- Interface that each resource manager must implement in order to be used in the WorkerManagerResourceSpotAllocation instance.
    ResourceManager.SortInterface<T extends GatheringSource>
    SortInterface.java --- Interface defining a sorter for gathering sources.
    ResourceManagerEntry
    ResourceManagerEntry.java --- The Interface that each worker that is going to be added to the IResourceManagers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MineralPatch
    MineralPatch.java --- Wrapper Class for mineral spots that are going to be managed by MineralPatchManager instances as GatheringSources.
    MineralPatchManager<T extends GatheringSource>
    MineralPatchManager.java --- ResourceManager for mineral fields.
    RefineryManager<T extends GatheringSource>
    RefineryManager.java --- ResourceManager for refineries.
    RefineryWrapper
    RefineryWrapper.java --- Wrapper Class for refineries that are going to be managed by RefineryManager instances as GatheringSources.
    ResourceManager<T extends GatheringSource>
    ResourceManager.java --- Manager class for a List of GatheringSources.
    WorkerManagerResourceSpotAllocation
    WorkerManagerResourceSpotAllocation.java --- The main Class managing the different ResourceManagers, mainly the one for minerals and the one for gas.
